<%
  is_user_representation = @representation_session.user_representation?
  represented_user = @representation_session.represented_user
  grant = @representation_session.trustee_grant
  scoped_collectives = if grant
    @other_collectives.select { |s| grant.allows_collective?(s) }
  else
    @other_collectives
  end
-%>
# Active representation session

<% if is_user_representation -%>
You are acting on behalf of **<%= represented_user&.display_name || represented_user&.handle %>** (@<%= represented_user&.handle %>).
<% else -%>
You are representing **<%= @collective.name %>** ([<%= @collective.path %>](<%= @collective.path %>)).
<% end -%>

Every action you take in this session is attributed to the represented entity and recorded in the session log.

| Field | Value |
|-------|-------|
| Session ID | `<%= @representation_session.id %>` |
| Short ID | `<%= @representation_session.truncated_id %>` |
| Started | <%= @representation_session.began_at.utc.strftime("%Y-%m-%d %H:%M UTC") %> |
| Expires | <%= @representation_session.expires_at.utc.strftime("%Y-%m-%d %H:%M UTC") %> |
| Type | <%= is_user_representation ? "User representation" : "Collective representation" %> |

<% if is_user_representation -%>
## Granted capabilities

<% if grant&.permissions.present? -%>
<% grant.permissions.each do |capability, enabled| -%>
<% next unless enabled -%>
- `<%= capability %>`
<% end -%>
<% else -%>
No specific capabilities granted.
<% end -%>

<% end -%>
## Available collectives

<% if scoped_collectives.empty? -%>
No other collectives are currently available within this session's scope.
<% else -%>
You can act <%= is_user_representation ? "on behalf of #{represented_user&.display_name}" : "as #{@collective.name}" %> in:

<% scoped_collectives.each do |c| -%>
- [<%= c.name %>](<%= c.path %>)
<% end -%>
<% end -%>

## Ending the session

To end this session, call `execute_action` with `end_representation` on the originating <%= is_user_representation ? "trustee grant" : "collective representation" %>, or send `DELETE /representing` with `X-Representation-Session-ID: <%= @representation_session.id %>`.
